cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) because it deals with generating image descriptions in different languages, which involves natural language processing. It is also likely to belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) because it deals with image captioning. Additionally, it may belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) because it proposes a reinforcement learning framework for generating cross-lingual image captions. Finally, it may belong to cs.MM (Multimedia) because it deals with image captioning corpora.
